{
  "id": "tde_astropy_integration_pipeline@1",
  "version": "1.0",
  "env_id": "kstars_sim_env@0.1",
  "description": "An automated observing sequence for the Tidal Disruption Event ASASSN-14li crashed overnight, leaving a partial dataset of FITS files. Complete the observation sequence using the observatory simulators and capture a sky view. Write a Python script using the 'astropy' library to parse all FITS files and compute a definitive integration summary. Refer to ~/Documents/tde_followup_brief.txt for specific parameters and required output paths.",
